      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIMPLY REIGN (1) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Maiden winner three back (16.99) at Casino over 300m. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. SAVANNAH STARS (2) was a winner (20.15) at this track two back but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Must be included in calculations. HI CHARLIE (7) turned in a better effort at Capalaba last start, finishing second behind Denim Beach (20.70) in a Grade 6. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Will give a great sight again. GOLDSTAR FOSTER (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole at this course and distance last start.",
